# Screenshots Storage Directory

This directory stores screenshots captured by XSS attacks.

## Security Notice

- This directory should have write permissions
- Screenshots are stored as PNG files
- Each screenshot includes metadata in screenshots_log.txt

## Directory Structure

```
screenshots/
├── screenshot_YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS_IP.png
├── screenshot_YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS_IP.png
└ └── ...
```

